<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.11">
<l>amararkaḷ toḻuteḻa alaikaṭal kaṭaintavaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yamarpoḻil vaḷaṅkuru kūrccaṭakōpaṉ kuṟ ṟēvalka</l>
<l>ḷamarcuvai yāyirat tavaṟṟiṉu ḷivaipattum vallā</l>
<l>ramararō ṭuyarviṟceṉ ṟaṟuvartam piṟaviyañ ciṟaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten among the thousand of abiding [sweet] taste,</l>
<l>the small services of Caṭakōpaṉ from fertile Kurukūr with suitable groves</l>
<l>on him who churned the rolling sea, while the immortals rose in worship,</l>
<l>they with go one height with the immortals [and] end the confinement in their births.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
